libbcu is a library to facilitate use of driver macusb


to build library cd to directory src and run:
  > make

to generate python binding set environment (bash, zsh):
  > source .rc
and run:
  > make py

to install library cd to directory src and:
  * set INSTDIR to required location in Makefile
  * update rule 'inst:' in Makefile
  * run:
      > make install
